Responsibility

Use of SBM in operational, infrastructure, AI, governance, industrial, financial, or safety-critical contexts is undertaken entirely at the user’s own responsibility.

SBM provides:

• deterministic structural state computation
• bounded horizon evaluation
• replay-verifiable artifact reproducibility
• structural alphabet discipline

It does not provide operational authority, regulatory certification, or safety guarantees.

